data.description: If you enjoy resort living, you will love Heron Bay Golf & Country Club. Heron Bay is a highly sought after community with lots of scenic sights, trails and a plethora of amenities. This gorgeous home has a 3 car garage with additional spacing. The formal living and dining room is perfect for entertaining. Cosy up at the fireplace in the Family room. The sizable kitchen won't disappoint, includes breakfast area and island. Private guest suite on the main level. Oversized recreation room on the 2nd level with large secondary bedrooms. If that's not enough, Seller has also included refrigerator, washer and dryer!!! Conveniently located near I-75, Tanger Outlet, Atlanta Motor Speedway and a host of restaurants.
